Vault Helm chart redistribution notice
======================================

The directory `chart/vault/` contains an unmodified copy of the official
HashiCorp Vault Helm chart, version 0.28.1 (app version 1.17.2):

    https://github.com/hashicorp/vault-helm
    https://helm.releases.hashicorp.com

The chart is licensed under MPL-2.0 — see `chart/vault/LICENSE` for the
full license text and `chart/vault/CHANGELOG.md` for upstream history.

The values files in `values/`, the LoadBalancer manifests in `manifests/`,
the helper PowerShell scripts (`recover-helm-chart.ps1`, `inspect-vault.ps1`),
and `README.md` are wrapper materials authored for this deployment and are
NOT part of the upstream chart.

To re-pull the chart fresh from the upstream:

    helm repo add hashicorp https://helm.releases.hashicorp.com
    helm pull hashicorp/vault --version 0.28.1 --untar
